<h2>Resources in This Category</h2>
<ul>

    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.bartleby.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Bartleby.com</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.bartleby.com/</strong></font> <br /> Search for famous quotes, classic literature, and nonfictional works. Site also includes dictionary, encyclopedia, and thesaurus.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.phaster.com/find_info_ref.html" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Ben's Phaster Online Reference Desk</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.phaster.com/find_info_ref.html</strong></font> <br /> Reference search guide. Research portal covers biography, dictionary, encyclopedia, language translation, thesaurus, world and city maps</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.bartleby.com/95/1.html" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Emily Post: Rules of Etiquette</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.bartleby.com/95/1.html</strong></font> <br /> Guide to good manners includes thousands of tips on correspondence, party giving, and conduct in every public or private setting.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.factmonster.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>FactMonster</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.factmonster.com/</strong></font> <br /> Includes searchable information related to sports, entertainment, geography, history, biography, education, and health.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.robertniles.com/data/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Finding Data on the Internet</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.robertniles.com/data/</strong></font> <br /> A journalist teaches other writers how to use the Internet to find facts.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.ipl.org/IPLBrowse/GetSubject?vid=12&amp;amp;cid=3&amp;amp;tid=4244&amp;amp;parent=0" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Internet Public Library Kidspace: Reference</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.ipl.org/IPLBrowse/GetSubject?vid=12&amp;amp;cid=3&amp;amp;tid=4244&amp;amp;parent=0</strong></font> <br /> General reference, including links to dictionaries, encyclopedias, and almanacs.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.martindalecenter.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Martindale's Reference Desk</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.martindalecenter.com/</strong></font> <br /> Massive collection of links to reference resources includes language centers, calculators, maps, science tables and important websites of various countries.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.refdesk.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>My Virtual Reference Desk</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.refdesk.com/</strong></font> <br /> Links to a variety of resources including news, weather, sports, encyclopedias, facts on file, FAQs, and tutorials.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.noodletools.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>NoodleTools</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.noodletools.com/</strong></font> <br /> A suite of interactive tools designed to aid students with their online research, from selecting a search engine and finding some relevant sources, to citing those sources.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://itools.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Research-It</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://itools.com/</strong></font> <br /> Look up the meaning of a word, find out when a famous person lived, or identify a foreign language at this one-stop research center.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.timeanddate.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Time and Date</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.timeanddate.com/</strong></font> <br /> Lots of time and date related information, such as yearly and monthly calendars, counters, countdown, and the world clock which shows the current time in cities all over the world.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://search.lib.virginia.edu/catalog" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Virgo</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://search.lib.virginia.edu/catalog</strong></font> <br /> Online archive includes over 45,000 classic texts in 12 languages.</p>
    </li>	
</ul>


